GroupAdminPending(uint256,address,addres.details: Event emitted when a group admin is being updated.

GroupAdminUpdated(uint256,address,addres.details: Event emitted when a new admin is assigned to a group.

GroupCreated(uint256).details: Event emitted when a new group is created.

MemberAdded(uint256,uint256,uint256,uint.details: Event emitted when a new identity commitment is added.

params.merkleTreeRoot: : New root hash of the tree.

MemberRemoved(uint256,uint256,uint256,ui.details: Event emitted when a new identity commitment is removed.

params.identityCommitment: : Existing identity commitment to be removed.
params.merkleTreeRoot: : New root hash of the tree.

MemberUpdated(uint256,uint256,uint256,ui.details: Event emitted when an identity commitment is updated.

params.identityCommitment: : Existing identity commitment to be updated.
params.merkleTreeRoot: : New root hash of the tree.

MembersAdded(uint256,uint256,uint256[],u.details: Event emitted when many identity commitments are added at the same time.

params.merkleTreeRoot: : New root hash of the tree.
params.startIndex: : Index of the first element of the new identity commitments in the merkle tree.

getGroupAdmin(uint256).details: Returns the address of the group admin. The group admin can be an Ethereum account or a smart contract.

getMerkleTreeDepth(uint256).details: Returns the depth of the tree of a group.

getMerkleTreeRoot(uint256).details: Returns the last root hash of a group.

getMerkleTreeSize(uint256).details: Returns the number of tree leaves of a group.

hasMember(uint256,uint256).details: Returns true if a member exists in a group.

returns._0: True if the member exists, false otherwise.

indexOf(uint256,uint256).details: Returns the index of a member.
